DngBU4bE6YtLWXhvchnCjA">Nhập cảnh hỷ vũ - 入境喜雨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Huy-Tr%E1%BB%A9/author-l-vfhV6KqRexQyEkpib8Ng">Đặng Huy Trứ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%C3%ADnh/Thanh-b%C3%ACnh-nh%E1%BA%A1c-Khu%C3%AA-t%C3%ACnh/poem-N4zl4Kf9-BqF20K6KZWoUg">Thanh bình nhạc - Khuê tình - 清平樂－閨情</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%C3%ADnh/author-karWQOvcFRKgjYjKdQQjKA">Lý Bính</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%A1n/T%E1%BB%91ng-b%C3%ACnh-t%C3%A2y-%C4%91%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%91c-Trang-%C4%90%E1%BB%8Bnh-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-v%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-chi%E1%BA%BFu-chinh-Chi%C3%AAm-Th%C3%A0nh/poem-3WrinDEzQncQevIUSKEOcA">Tống bình tây đô đốc Trang Định đại vương phụng chiếu chinh Chiêm Thành - 送平西都督莊定大王奉詔征占城</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%A1n/author-h_HbFCmxWKkwxboqzaEfNA">Trần Nguyên Đán</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Th%C3%A0nh-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i/T%E1%BB%A9-th%C3%AC-%C4%91i%E1%BB%81n-vi%C3%AAn-t%E1%BA%A1p-h%E1%BB%A9ng-V%C3%A3n-xu%C3%A2n-k%E1%BB%B3-11/poem-45EmXH6mAGVEkhAXbZDvOw">Tứ thì điền viên tạp hứng - Vãn xuân kỳ 11 - 四時田園雜興－晚春其十一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Th%C3%A0nh-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i/author-ppK7YKfOyDZw9vIHLHbJVA">Phạm Thành Đại</a>)<br></div>	</div>
